Package: baize-kube
Version: 1.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Jean Boutros <jean.boutros@if-you-know-you-know.com>
Depends: podman, curl, systemd
Description: Rootless minikube cluster service for Raspberry Pi
 Provisions a dedicated system user (baize) that owns and runs a rootless
 minikube cluster via Podman at boot using systemd user services with
 lingering. Configures cgroup v2 memory delegation and grants cluster
 read access to the baize-consumers group.
